node.text:
<@existentialcrisisboy> 
❤️‍🔥APPRECIATION POST❤️‍🔥
I am so grateful for your presence in my life. The fact that we’ve single handedly produced THREE FULL ALBUMS together (playing all the parts of a 5 piece band between the two of us) is MIND BLOWING 🥺🙏🏾 THANK YOU for your endless patience and creativity 💕Can’t wait to make more albums and memories with you!
